<h2 class="p1">OhioNET's Community Collaboration Teams</h2>
<p class="normal">We're fostering conversations that extend across library types.  Our inaugural Community Collaboration Teams--<strong>Team Vittles</strong> and <strong>Building Bridges for College Success</strong>--are making great progress on their projects. <a href="https://www.ohionet.org/blog/2017/08/grassroots-conversations-are-growing-ohionet-community-collaboration-teams"><strong>CLICK HERE</strong></a> for an overview.</p>

<h2 class="p1">Select from 5 Training Tracks</h2>
<p class="normal">We're pleased to announce that beginning in 2018 OhioNET will be offering 5 training tracks to choose from.  Check out our Training Calendar for a full listing of all our upcoming continuing education events: <a href="https://www.ohionet.org/training-calendar"><strong>https://www.ohionet.org/training-calendar</strong></a></p>
